	<ThingDef ParentName="ApparelArmorPowerBase">
		<defName>FRS_Apparel_RedArmyStealthSuit</defName>
		<label>PLA Stealth Suit</label> 
		<description>An advanced stealth suit designed and manufactured by Chinese scientists to counter the American power armor suits. It features the most advanced cloaking technology ever devised and can make its wearer virtually invisible. While the tight black suit is significantly more protective than clothing, it’s not made to withstand a whole lot of damage.</description>
